  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Doll, Football, Pillow, Stick, ToiletPaper, ToyCar

    public class Toy
extends Item
    Extends the Item class and provides the methods required for toys to function in game. All instances of Food should be created on a subclass level eg. Doll doll = new Doll(); All methods required for the function of any children are provided in this class.
